<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<title>I'm Sorry 💔</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>

/* =============================================
   RESET
============================================= */
*, *::before, *::after { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

/* =============================================
   ROOT VARIABLES
============================================= */
:root {
  --red:    #ff0033;
  --rose:   #ff3366;
  --bg:     #000000;
  --card:   #111111;
  --card2:  #191919;
  --white:  #ffffff;
  --gray:   #888888;
  --lgray:  #cccccc;
  --glow:   rgba(255,0,51,.35);
}

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--white);
  font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
  overflow-x: hidden;
  -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
}

/* =============================================
   SCROLL PROGRESS BAR
============================================= */
#progress {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0; left: 0;
  height: 3px;
  width: 0%;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--red), var(--rose));
  box-shadow: 0 0 14px var(--red);
  z-index: 9999;
  transition: width .08s linear;
}

/* =============================================
   FLOATING PARTICLES
============================================= */
#ptcl-wrap {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.ptcl {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -30px;
  animation: ptcl-rise linear infinite;
  opacity: 0;
  user-select: none;
}
@keyframes ptcl-rise {
  0%   { transform: translateY(0) scale(.6) rotate(0deg);  opacity: 0; }
  8%   { opacity: .6; }
  88%  { opacity: .3; }
  100% { transform: translateY(-110vh) scale(1.1) rotate(25deg); opacity: 0; }
}

/* =============================================
   SECTIONS
============================================= */
section {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  padding: 48px 20px;
}

/* =============================================
   REVEAL ANIMATION
============================================= */
.reveal {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(44px);
  transition:
    opacity  .75s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1),
    transform .75s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1);
}
.reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.d1 { transition-delay: .10s; }
.d2 { transition-delay: .20s; }
.d3 { transition-delay: .30s; }
.d4 { transition-delay: .40s; }

/* =============================================
   HERO
============================================= */
#hero {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 40px 24px 80px;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 55% at 50% 50%, rgba(255,0,50,.09) 0%, transparent 70%);
  overflow: hidden;
}

#rain-canvas {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  width: 100%; height: 100%;
  pointer-events: none;
  opacity: .28;
}

.hero-title {
  font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 14vw, 5.5rem);
  font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--red);
  letter-spacing: 6px;
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  text-shadow:
    0 0 20px var(--red),
    0 0 60px rgba(255,0,50,.75),
    0 0 130px rgba(255,0,50,.45);
  animation: neon-flicker 2.8s ease-in-out infinite;
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
}

.hero-emojis {
  font-size: 2.8rem;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  animation: float-bob 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
}

#typewriter {
  font-size: clamp(.95rem, 4.5vw, 1.25rem);
  color: var(--lgray);
  font-weight: 300;
  min-height: 2rem;
  letter-spacing: .5px;
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
}
#typewriter::after {
  content: '|';
  color: var(--red);
  animation: blink .8s step-end infinite;
}

.scroll-cue {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 28px; left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.22);
  font-size: .62rem;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  z-index: 1;
}
.scroll-arrow {
  width: 16px; height: 16px;
  border-right: 2px solid rgba(255,0,51,.4);
  border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255,0,51,.4);
  transform: rotate(45deg);
  animation: arrow-fall 1.6s ease-in-out infinite;
}

/* =============================================
   GIF SECTION
============================================= */
#gifs { padding: 20px 20px 40px; }

.gif-row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  justify-content: center;
  max-width: 440px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.gif-box {
  flex: 1;
  min-width: 0;
  border-radius: 18px;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,0,51,.14);
  background: var(--card);
  aspect-ratio: 1;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

.gif-box img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  display: block;
}

/* =============================================
   EMOTIONAL CARDS
============================================= */
#emotion-cards { padding: 8px 20px 36px; }

.em-stack {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 14px;
  max-width: 440px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.em-card {
  background: var(--card);
  border-radius: 22px;
  padding: 28px 22px;
  text-align: center;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,0,51,.07);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
}

.em-card.red-glow {
  background: linear-gradient(160deg,#120a0e,#111111);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,0,51,.2);
  box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,0,51,.06), 0 4px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
}

.em-emoji { font-size: 3rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.em-card:nth-child(1) .em-emoji { animation: heartbreak-shake 1.8s ease-in-out infinite; }
.em-card:nth-child(2) .em-emoji { animation: pleading-wobble 1.6s ease-in-out infinite; }
.em-card:nth-child(3) .em-emoji { animation: matter-float 2.2s ease-in-out infinite; }
.em-card:nth-child(4) .em-emoji {
  animation: heartbeat .95s ease-in-out infinite;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 14px rgba(255,0,51,.7));
}

.em-title { font-size: 1.32rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 9px; }
.em-text  { font-size: .88rem; color: var(--lgray); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.65; }

/* =============================================
   PHOTO SECTION
============================================= */
#photo-section { padding: 8px 20px 36px; }

.photo-card {
  background: var(--card);
  border-radius: 22px;
  padding: 28px 22px;
  max-width: 440px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,0,51,.12);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.6);
}

.photo-frame {
  width: 190px; height: 190px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin: 0 auto 22px;
  border: 3px solid var(--red);
  box-shadow: 0 0 28px var(--glow), 0 0 70px rgba(255,0,51,.1);
}

.photo-frame img {
  width: 100%; height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  display: block;
}

.photo-title { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.photo-sub   { font-size: .9rem; color: var(--lgray); font-weight: 300; }

/* =============================================
   VIDEO SECTION
============================================= */
#video-section { padding: 8px 20px 36px; }

.video-heading {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.video-wrap {
  max-width: 440px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  border-radius: 20px;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 2px solid rgba(255,0,51,.18);
  box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(255,0,51,.07);
  background: #050505;
}

.video-wrap video {
  width: 100%;
  display: block;
  max-height: 72vh;
}

/* =============================================
   SONG SECTION
============================================= */
#song-section { padding: 8px 20px 36px; }

.sec-title {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.song-card {
  max-width: 440px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  background: linear-gradient(145deg,#120a12,#0d0d0d);
  border-radius: 22px;
  padding: 26px 22px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,0,51,.18);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.song-blob {
  position: absolute;
  top: -40px; right: -40px;
  width: 180px; height: 180px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle,rgba(255,0,51,.07) 0%,transparent 65%);
  animation: blob-drift 7s ease-in-out infinite;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.song-header {
  display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
}

.song-disc {
  width: 66px; height: 66px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: conic-gradient(#ff0033, #550011, #ff3366, #ff0033);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  animation: disc-spin 4s linear infinite;
  box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(255,0,51,.5);
  position: relative;
}

.song-disc::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  width: 22px; height: 22px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--card);
  border: 2px solid rgba(255,0,51,.3);
}

.song-meta   { flex: 1; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.song-name   { font-size: .98rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.song-artist { font-size: .78rem; color: var(--gray); }

.song-tagline {
  font-size: .8rem; color: #aaa; font-style: italic;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);
  padding-top: 14px;
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
}

.viz {
  display: flex; gap: 4px;
  align-items: flex-end;
  height: 34px;
  justify-content: center;
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
}
.viz-bar {
  width: 5px; border-radius: 3px;
  background: linear-gradient(0deg, var(--red), var(--rose));
  animation: viz-dance .75s ease-in-out infinite;
  transform-origin: bottom;
}
.viz-bar:nth-child(1){height:45%;animation-delay:.00s}
.viz-bar:nth-child(2){height:85%;animation-delay:.07s}
.viz-bar:nth-child(3){height:35%;animation-delay:.14s}
.viz-bar:nth-child(4){height:70%;animation-delay:.21s}
.viz-bar:nth-child(5){height:100%;animation-delay:.09s}
.viz-bar:nth-child(6){height:52%;animation-delay:.28s}
.viz-bar:nth-child(7){height:78%;animation-delay:.17s}
.viz-bar:nth-child(8){height:40%;animation-delay:.03s}
.viz-bar:nth-child(9){height:62%;animation-delay:.25s}

/* =============================================
   GALLERY OF PERFECTION
============================================= */
#gallery { padding: 8px 20px 36px; }

.gallery-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 10px;
  max-width: 440px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.g-item {
  border-radius: 16px;
  overflow: hidden;
  aspect-ratio: 1;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);
  background: #0a0a0a;
  position: relative;
}

.g-item:first-child {
  grid-column: 1 / -1;
  aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
}

.g-item img {
  width: 100%; height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  display: block;
  transition: transform .4s ease;
}

.g-item:active img { transform: scale(1.06); }

/* =============================================
   HEARTFELT MESSAGE
============================================= */
#heartfelt { padding: 8px 20px 36px; }

.hf-card {
  max-width: 440px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  background: linear-gradient(160deg,#130810,#0f0f0f);
  border-radius: 22px;
  padding: 32px 24px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,0,51,.15);
  text-align: center;
  box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(255,0,51,.04);
}

.hf-icon {
  font-size: 2.8rem;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  animation: heartbeat 1.1s ease-in-out infinite;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 14px rgba(255,0,51,.6));
}

.hf-section-title {
  font-size: 1.45rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 22px;
}

.hf-para {
  font-size: .9rem;
  color: var(--lgray);
  line-height: 1.9;
  font-weight: 300;
  text-align: left;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}

.hf-para:last-of-type { margin-bottom: 0; }

.hf-divider {
  width: 40px; height: 2px;
  background: var(--red);
  margin: 18px auto;
  border-radius: 2px;
  opacity: .5;
}

/* =============================================
   PROMISES
============================================= */
#promises { padding: 8px 20px 36px; }

.promises-wrap { max-width: 440px; margin: 0 auto; }

.promises-heading {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 22px;
}

.p-card {
  background: var(--card2);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 17px 18px;
  margin-bottom: 11px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 13px;
  border-left: 3px solid var(--red);
  box-shadow: 0 3px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateX(-32px);
  transition: opacity .5s ease, transform .5s ease;
}

.p-card.in { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }

.p-icon { font-size: 1.2rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
.p-text { font-size: .87rem; color: var(--lgray); line-height: 1.55; font-weight: 300; }

/* =============================================
   CTA SECTION
============================================= */
#cta {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 50px 24px 100px;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 90% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(255,0,50,.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
}

.cta-pre {
  font-size: .82rem;
  color: var(--gray);
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.cta-question {
  font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 5.5vw, 1.8rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 36px;
  line-height: 1.3;
}

.wa-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  background: linear-gradient(140deg, #ff0033, #cc001a);
  color: #fff;
  padding: 20px 44px;
  border-radius: 50px;
  font-size: 1.02rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .4px;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow:
    0 0 32px rgba(255,0,51,.6),
    0 0 80px rgba(255,0,51,.22),
    inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.12);
  animation: btn-throb 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  transition: transform .15s ease;
  text-decoration: none;
}

.wa-btn::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: -100%;
  width: 100%; height: 100%;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,.2), transparent);
  animation: sweep 2.8s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.wa-btn:active { transform: scale(.96); }

/* =============================================
   KEYFRAMES
============================================= */
@keyframes neon-flicker {
  0%,100% {
    text-shadow:0 0 20px var(--red),0 0 60px rgba(255,0,50,.75),0 0 130px rgba(255,0,50,.45);
  }
  48% {
    text-shadow:0 0 28px var(--red),0 0 80px rgba(255,0,50,.85),0 0 160px rgba(255,0,50,.55);
  }
  50% {
    text-shadow:0 0 14px var(--red),0 0 38px rgba(255,0,50,.4),0 0 70px rgba(255,0,50,.22);
  }
  52% {
    text-shadow:0 0 28px var(--red),0 0 80px rgba(255,0,50,.85),0 0 160px rgba(255,0,50,.55);
  }
}

@keyframes float-bob {
  0%,100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  50%      { transform: translateY(-12px); }
}

@keyframes blink {
  0%,100% { opacity: 1; }
  50%      { opacity: 0; }
}

@keyframes arrow-fall {
  0%,100% { transform: rotate(45deg) translateY(0); opacity:.4; }
  50%      { transform: rotate(45deg) translateY(6px); opacity:.8; }
}

@keyframes heartbeat {
  0%,100% { transform: scale(1); }
  14%      { transform: scale(1.2); }
  28%      { transform: scale(1); }
  42%      { transform: scale(1.12); }
  56%      { transform: scale(1); }
}

@keyframes heartbreak-shake {
  0%,100% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0); }
  30%      { transform: scale(1.07) rotate(-4deg); }
  60%      { transform: scale(.93) rotate(4deg); }
}

@keyframes pleading-wobble {
  0%,100% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0); }
  25%      { transform: scale(1.1) rotate(-6deg); }
  75%      { transform: scale(.95) rotate(6deg); }
}

@keyframes matter-float {
  0%,100% { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
  50%      { transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.05); }
}

@keyframes disc-spin {
  from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
  to   { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}

@keyframes viz-dance {
  0%,100% { transform: scaleY(.32); }
  50%      { transform: scaleY(1); }
}

@keyframes blob-drift {
  0%,100% { transform: translate(0,0) scale(1); }
  50%      { transform: translate(-10px,12px) scale(1.1); }
}

@keyframes btn-throb {
  0%,100% {
    box-shadow:0 0 32px rgba(255,0,51,.6),0 0 80px rgba(255,0,51,.22),
               inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.12);
  }
  50% {
    box-shadow:0 0 55px rgba(255,0,51,.85),0 0 130px rgba(255,0,51,.42),
               inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.12);
  }
}

@keyframes sweep {
  0%       { left: -100%; }
  45%,100% { left: 100%; }
}

/* =============================================
   REDUCED MOTION
============================================= */
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *, *::before, *::after { animation: none !important; transition: none !important; }
  .reveal { opacity: 1 !important; transform: none !important; }
  .p-card { opacity: 1 !important; transform: none !important; }
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- Scroll progress bar -->
<div id="progress"></div>

<!-- Floating heart particles background -->
<div id="ptcl-wrap"></div>


<!-- ============================================================
     SECTION 1 · HERO
============================================================ -->
<section id="hero">
  <canvas id="rain-canvas"></canvas>

  <h1 class="hero-title">SORRYYYYY</h1>
  <span class="hero-emojis">😭 ❤️</span>
  <p id="typewriter"></p>

  <div class="scroll-cue">
    <span>scroll</span>
    <div class="scroll-arrow"></div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============================================================
     SECTION 2 · GIF ROW
     ► Put gif1.gif · gif2.gif · gif3.gif in the same folder
============================================================ -->
<section id="gifs">
  <div class="gif-row">
    <div class="gif-box reveal">
      <img src="gif1.gif" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="gif-box reveal d1">
      <img src="gif2.gif" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="gif-box reveal d2">
      <img src="gif3.gif" alt="">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============================================================
     SECTION 3 · EMOTIONAL CARDS
============================================================ -->
<section id="emotion-cards">
  <div class="em-stack">

    <div class="em-card reveal">
      <span class="em-emoji">💔</span>
      <h3 class="em-title">It Was My Fault</h3>
      <p class="em-text">I realize my words hurt you deeply. No excuses, no justifications — just a genuine, heartfelt sorry.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="em-card reveal d1">
      <span class="em-emoji">🥺</span>
      <h3 class="em-title">Please Don't Stay Mad</h3>
      <p class="em-text">Everything feels off without you. The world honestly makes no sense when you're upset with me.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="em-card reveal d2">
      <span class="em-emoji">❤️</span>
      <h3 class="em-title">You Matter</h3>
      <p class="em-text">You are the most important part of my life. I don't take that lightly — not for a single second.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="em-card red-glow reveal d3">
      <span class="em-emoji">❤️</span>
      <h3 class="em-title">My Heart Beats For You ❤️</h3>
      <p class="em-text">Please let go of the anger... I miss you more than any words can ever explain.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============================================================
     SECTION 4 · PHOTO
     ► Put your photo as image.png in the same folder
============================================================ -->
<section id="photo-section">
  <div class="photo-card reveal">
    <div class="photo-frame">
      <img src="image.png" alt="Photo">
    </div>
    <h3 class="photo-title">SORRYYYYY 😭</h3>
    <p class="photo-sub">Just one forgiveness please... that's all I'm asking for.</p>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============================================================
     SECTION 5 · VIDEO
     ► Put your video as video.mp4 in the same folder
============================================================ -->
<section id="video-section">
  <p class="video-heading reveal">Just Watch This ❤️</p>
  <div class="video-wrap reveal d1">
    <video controls playsinline preload="metadata">
      <source src="video.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    </video>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============================================================
     SECTION 6 · SONG DEDICATED TO YOU
     ► Edit song name & artist below
============================================================ -->
<section id="song-section">
  <p class="sec-title reveal">🎵 A Song Dedicated To You</p>
  <div class="song-card reveal d1">
    <div class="song-blob"></div>
    <div class="song-header">
      <div class="song-disc">🎵</div>
